          "{{base_url}}"
        ],
        "path": [
          "api",
          "auth",
          "impersonate"
        ]
      },
      "description": "Create a tenant impersonation URL for a workspace the authenticated central user can access.\n\n**Auth:** requires authenticated central session/token (`auth:central-api`).\n\n**Query params:** none\n\n**Request body validation:**\n- `tenant`: required|string|max:255 (tenant slug)\n- `redirect_url`: sometimes|string|max:2048|starts_with:/\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Requires either direct tenant membership or `support`/`super_admin` role\n- Requires mapped active tenant account for the central user\n- Returns a tenant API impersonation URL and token"
    },
